cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.PL, cs.SE 

This paper deals with epistemic logic and dynamic operators to describe information changing events. It discusses the execution of events in information states modeled as pointed Kripke models. These topics are closely related to the areas of logic (cs.LO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), programming languages (cs.PL), and software engineering (cs.SE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
